### Variables
@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000/sales/api
@customerToken = TU_TOKEN_CUSTOMER
@adminToken = TU_TOKEN_ADMIN
@addressId = 1

### ==========================================
### ADDRESS
### ==========================================

### Get countries (público ✅)
GET {{baseUrl}}/address/countries HTTP/1.1

### ==========================================

### Get my addresses (customer ✅)
GET {{baseUrl}}/address/ HTTP/1.1
Authorization: Bearer {{customerToken}}

### ==========================================

### Get address by ID (customer ✅)
GET {{baseUrl}}/address/{{addressId}} HTTP/1.1
Authorization: Bearer {{customerToken}}

### ==========================================

### Create address (válido ✅)
POST {{baseUrl}}/address/ HTTP/1.1
Authorization: Bearer {{customerToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "number": "123",
    "street": "Av. Los Pinos",
    "address_line_1": "Dpto 4B",
    "address_line_2": null,
    "city": "Lima",
    "state_province": "Lima",
    "postal_code": "15001",
    "country_id": 1
}

### ==========================================

### Create address (country_id no existe — 422 ❌)
POST {{baseUrl}}/address/ HTTP/1.1
Authorization: Bearer {{customerToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "number": "123",
    "street": "Av. Los Pinos",
    "city": "Lima",
    "state_province": "Lima",
    "postal_code": "15001",
    "country_id": 999
}

### ==========================================

### Update address (válido ✅)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/address/{{addressId}} HTTP/1.1
Authorization: Bearer {{customerToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "number": "456",
    "street": "Av. Javier Prado",
    "city": "Lima",
    "state_province": "Lima",
    "postal_code": "15046",
    "country_id": 1
}

### ==========================================

### Set default address (válido ✅)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/address/{{addressId}}/default HTTP/1.1
Authorization: Bearer {{customerToken}}

### ==========================================

### Delete address (válido ✅)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/address/{{addressId}} HTTP/1.1
Authorization: Bearer {{customerToken}}

### ==========================================

### Sin token → 401 ❌
GET {{baseUrl}}/address/ HTTP/1.1

### ==========================================

### Con token admin → 403 ❌
GET {{baseUrl}}/address/ HTTP/1.1
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### ==========================================
### ADMIN — Ver direcciones de un customer
### ==========================================

### GET customer addresses (admin ✅)
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/customers/UUID_DEL_CUSTOMER/addresses HTTP/1.1
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}